data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom twin home is a highly sought after model for many reasons including its convenient location near the high school.This home is very spacious with over 2000 sq ft of living space!  The main floor is open concept.  Living room has beautiful built in hickory entertainment center.  Behind double doors just off the living room is a flex room that could be used as an office, den, game room, playroom or a sleeping area if a main floor bedroom is needed.  Large kitchen is a fantastic gathering space and features lots of gorgeous hickory cabinets with open cubicles to show off collectables!  The island has plenty of room for seating.  Appliances are included in the sale.   A full bathroom and laundry room are also on the main floor.  Laundry room has more beautiful hickory cabinets, a bench with open storage underneath and a sink.  Washer/dryer are included in the sale.5.  The upper level includes a large primary suite with 5 piece  bathroom & walk in closet.  Three additional bedrooms and another full bath complete 2nd story.A sprinkler system makes watering a breeze.  The backyard is fenced and includes a garden area.  Attached 2 car garage is spacious!  Call your Realtor to schedule a showing!
